{"parse":{"title":"Sharkham Point Iron Mine","pageid":55332041,"revid":802558207,"text":{"*":"<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox vcard\" style=\"width:22em\"><caption class=\"fn org\">Sharkham Point Iron Mine</caption><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/wiki/File:Sharkham_Point_Mine_Adit.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Sharkham Point Mine Adit.jpg\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/b6/Sharkham_Point_Mine_Adit.jpg/220px-Sharkham_Point_Mine_Adit.jpg\" width=\"220\" height=\"165\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/b6/Sharkham_Point_Mine_Adit.jpg/330px-Sharkham_Point_Mine_Adit.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/b6/Sharkham_Point_Mine_Adit.jpg/440px-Sharkham_Point_Mine_Adit.jpg 2x\" data-file-width=\"5152\" data-file-height=\"3864\" /></a><div>An adit of the mine</div></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">Location</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<div class=\"center\"><div style=\"width:220px;float:none;clear:both;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\"><div style=\"width:220px;padding:0\"><div style=\"position:relative;width:220px\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:Devon_UK_location_map.svg\" class=\"image\" title=\"Sharkham Point Iron Mine is located in Devon\"><img alt=\"Sharkham Point Iron Mine is located in Devon\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/ab/Devon_UK_location_map.svg/220px-Devon_UK_location_map.svg.png\" width=\"220\" height=\"202\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/ab/Devon_UK_location_map.svg/330px-Devon_UK_location_map.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/ab/Devon_UK_location_map.svg/440px-Devon_UK_location_map.svg.png 2x\" data-file-width=\"1292\" data-file-height=\"1187\" /></a><div style=\"position:absolute;top:80.553%;left:65.704%\"><div style=\"position:absolute;left:-6px;top:-6px;line-height:0\"><img alt=\"Sharkham Point Iron Mine\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/ac/Schlaegel_und_Eisen_nach_DIN_21800.svg/12px-Schlaegel_und_Eisen_nach_DIN_21800.svg.png\" title=\"Sharkham Point Iron Mine\" width=\"12\" height=\"12\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/ac/Schlaegel_und_Eisen_nach_DIN_21800.svg/18px-Schlaegel_und_Eisen_nach_DIN_21800.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/ac/Schlaegel_und_Eisen_nach_DIN_21800.svg/24px-Schlaegel_und_Eisen_nach_DIN_21800.svg.png 2x\" data-file-width=\"354\" data-file-height=\"354\" /></div><div style=\"font-size:90%;line-height:110%;position:absolute;width:6em;top:-0.75em;left:7px;text-align:left\"><div style=\"display:inline;padding:1px;float:left\">Sharkham Point Iron Mine</div></div></div></div><div></div></div></div></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Location</th><td class=\"label\">\nSharkham Point</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">County</th><td>\nDevon</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Country</th><td>\nEngland</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Coordinates</th><td>\n<span class=\"plainlinks nourlexpansion\"><a class=\"external text\" href=\"//tools.wmflabs.org/geohack/geohack.php?pagename=Sharkham_Point_Iron_Mine&amp;params=50.3817_N_3.4979_W_type:landmark_region:GB-DEV\"><span class=\"geo-nondefault\"><span class=\"geo-dms\" title=\"Maps, aerial photos, and other data for this location\"><span class=\"latitude\">50\u00b022\u203254\u2033N</span> <span class=\"longitude\">3\u00b029\u203252\u2033W</span></span></span><span class=\"geo-multi-punct\">&#xfeff; / &#xfeff;</span><span class=\"geo-default\"><span class=\"geo-dec\" title=\"Maps, aerial photos, and other data for this location\">50.3817\u00b0N 3.4979\u00b0W</span><span style=\"display:none\">&#xfeff; / <span class=\"geo\">50.3817; -3.4979</span></span></span></a></span><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span id=\"coordinates\"><a href=\"/wiki/Geographic_coordinate_system\" title=\"Geographic coordinate system\">Coordinates</a>: <span class=\"plainlinks nourlexpansion\"><a class=\"external text\" href=\"//tools.wmflabs.org/geohack/geohack.php?pagename=Sharkham_Point_Iron_Mine&amp;params=50.3817_N_3.4979_W_type:landmark_region:GB-DEV\"><span class=\"geo-nondefault\"><span class=\"geo-dms\" title=\"Maps, aerial photos, and other data for this location\"><span class=\"latitude\">50\u00b022\u203254\u2033N</span> <span class=\"longitude\">3\u00b029\u203252\u2033W</span></span></span><span class=\"geo-multi-punct\">&#xfeff; / &#xfeff;</span><span class=\"geo-default\"><span class=\"geo-dec\" title=\"Maps, aerial photos, and other data for this location\">50.3817\u00b0N 3.4979\u00b0W</span><span style=\"display:none\">&#xfeff; / <span class=\"geo\">50.3817; -3.4979</span></span></span></a></span></span></span></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">Production</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Products</th><td class=\"category\">\nHematite</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Type</th><td class=\"category\">\nOpencast and underground</td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">History</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Opened</th><td>\nc1790<span style=\"display:none\">&#160;(<span class=\"bday dtstart published updated\">c1790</span>)</span></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Closed</th><td>\n1914<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><span style=\"display:none\">&#160;(<span class=\"dtend\">1914<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></span>)</span></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Sharkham Point Iron Mine</b> was an <a href=\"/wiki/Iron_mine\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Iron mine\">iron mine</a> at <a href=\"/wiki/Sharkham_Point\" title=\"Sharkham Point\">Sharkham Point</a>, near the town of <a href=\"/wiki/Brixham\" title=\"Brixham\">Brixham</a> in <a href=\"/wiki/Devon\" title=\"Devon\">Devon</a>. The mine was worked for around 125 years and employed at its peak 100 workers. It was primarily an <a href=\"/wiki/Open-cast_mine\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Open-cast mine\">open cast mine</a>, but five <a href=\"/wiki/Mine_shaft\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Mine shaft\">shafts</a> and six <a href=\"/wiki/Adit\" title=\"Adit\">adits</a> are also mentioned in reports of the site. Some are still accessible today, but since the area was used as a <a href=\"/wiki/Landfill\" title=\"Landfill\">rubbish tip</a> in the 1950s and 60s, much of the archaeology has been covered over.<sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Sharkham_Point_Iron_Mine&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: History\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The first reliably attributable reference to an iron deposit at Sharkham Point appears to have been made by Henry De la Beche in his memoir of 1839 where he said: \"A large iron-lode runs nearly east and west from Sharkham Point, near Brixham, to Upton, and was extensively worked towards the end of 1837\"<sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>.\n</p><p>The mining of iron ore at Sharkham Point was however underway as early as 1790 when a discovery of \"considerable quantities of kidney ore\" was reported. A century later at the peak period of operation the mine employed 100 workers and shipped ore to South Wales and West Hartlepool for smelting<sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>.\n</p><p>It was reported that mining (by the Brixham Hematite Iron Mining Company Ltd) ceased at Sharkham Point in 1914-15<sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>. This marked the period when the mining industry across the whole of the south-west region finally reached the point of large scale economic collapse. However, in common with other mines some dump picking may have continued into the 1930s.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Sharkham_Point_Iron_Mine&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"reflist\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal;\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://ougs.org/local_geology/article.php?id=141&amp;&amp;branchcode=swe\">\"Sharkham iron mine\"</a>. <i>ougs.org</i><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">24 September</span> 2017</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=ougs.org&amp;rft.atitle=Sharkham+iron+mine&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fougs.org%2Flocal_geology%2Farticle.php%3Fid%3D141%26%26branchcode%3Dswe&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ASharkham+Point+Iron+Mine\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.mindat.org/loc-34371.html\">\"Sharkham Point Mine, Brixham, South Devon, Devon, England, UK\"</a>. <i>www.mindat.org</i><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">24 September</span> 2017</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fm